{"tid":2236021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地母放任2小孩踢電影銀幕 戲院需停開半個月","createTime":"2020-10-09T07:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T09:05:53.000Z","uid":271829,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6e30e1b30226258dc5f1d1890fd782782ad4ec69","tid":2236021,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BiRkI-DaNyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBiRkI-DaNyM&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzrHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=4fb66675\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BiRkI-DaNyM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/06c03f839b757a89a75915d0134fe248/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201009/_2020100912152142893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F06c03f839b757a89a75915d0134fe248%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201009%2F_2020100912152142893.jpg&h=41fec483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地有家長帶兩名小孩去看電影時，放任他們不斷大力踢銀幕，導致受損部分無法使用。網圖<br />\n<br />\n內地「十一」黃金周長假期間，不少人都湧到戲院看電影。不過，海南省海口市有一名家長近日帶兩名小孩去看電影時，竟放任他們不斷大力踢銀幕，導致受損部分無法使用，戲院半個月內亦無法開放，損失慘重！<br />\n<br />\n當地一段閉路電視片段在網上瘋傳，影片中可見，有兩名小孩在影廳內的空座位上爬來爬去，其中一人更對銀幕又打又踢，而他們的家長沒有出現在畫面上，全程竟也沒有阻止這兩名「破壞王」。<br />\n<br />\n戲院負責人楊先生表示，該場次的票只售出3張，當時的工作人員亦沒有發現銀幕有損壞，只在事後發現銀幕上出現很多腳印，查看閉路電視畫面後事件才曝光。他續指，小孩狂踢銀幕，令銀幕表層的金屬粉脫落，投射上去的影像會變形，而銀幕造價約1萬元人民幣（即約1.2萬港元），製作需時半個月，意味戲院短時間內難以重新開放，損失嚴重。雙方目前正就賠償事宜協商中。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後引起網上熱議，不少人都批評該兩名小孩，「怎麼像個野人一樣」、「家長和孩子都是沒家教的」、「什麼讓你覺得，你家小孩禍害別人的東西完全無所謂呢？」、「家長的默許態度，與這個孩子瘋狂的樣子，完美匹配」。"},{"pid":"9633646736f4cae091be3e5e3b5ec0ab19c8d0fd","tid":2236021,"uid":30524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成間戲院得一個House架咩?<br />\n咁就要停業半個月?"},{"pid":"70d6206b53d389b9340f54ce52127cbdf8ebed47","tid":2236021,"uid":11598,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />生番 下下who 下下who"},{"pid":"9bc1ae4cfc445461b4d4c69afcf1b4d44b7018a0","tid":2236021,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"當代花木蘭s<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cf3c98d657381039ce7ddd6d4d6aa089119229","tid":2236021,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"原來戲院都有CCTV"},{"pid":"0b6ba755cc317533d8395007a4a059eaa2767bde","tid":2236021,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43cf3c98d657381039ce7ddd6d4d6aa089119229","tid":2236021,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"原來戲院都有CCTV"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e94abd134bf88b53692ba784af261f2a2ac265","tid":2236021,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"踢兩踢就爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b0289a2d065b563e96b24e21eccdd2feb65a4f","tid":2236021,"uid":303436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"會咁容易就爛？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c4fe85770b951b20ddd51418add5418caac6fe","tid":2236021,"uid":364850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9633646736f4cae091be3e5e3b5ec0ab19c8d0fd","tid":2236021,"uid":30524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成間戲院得一個House架咩?<br />\n咁就要停業半個月?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"同撞車一樣 硬食<br />\n一陣上庭 claim 保險你仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.